title: Parcels
description:
Parcel Polygons. The dataset contains locations and
attributes of Parcels, created as part of the Polk County Geographic
Information System (Polk County GIS). The tax information (attribution) comes

automated, occurs nightly, and uses the most currently available tax
information.??
